        {
            "title": "川普宣布就格陵蘭達成未來協議的「框架」 不實施先前威脅的關稅",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國總統唐納德·川普表示，他將不對反對美國獲得<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:格陵蘭;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/格陵蘭\">格陵蘭</a>的歐洲國家加徵關稅，並稱他已就該島達成了「未來協議的框架」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「基於我與北約秘書長馬克·呂特進行的一次非常富有成效的會晤，我們已就格陵蘭，事實上整個北極地區，形成了未來協議的框架，」 川普周三在社交媒體上發文稱。「基於此，我將不會實施原定於2月1日生效的關稅。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普此前威脅稱，如果8個歐洲國家不接受他得到格陵蘭的訴求，他將對這些國家的產品加徵關稅。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-22c5a66d-b271-32a4-8060-d377d5c9b0ad-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位美國總統還表示，將就金穹飛彈防禦系統進行進一步討論。他曾稱，美國控制格陵蘭對支持該系統至關重要。川普補充稱，副總統范斯、國務卿盧比奧、特使威特科夫以及「其他若干人」等將負責談判。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Holding Off on Greenland Tariffs, Citing ‘Framework’ Deal</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%B0%B1%E6%A0%BC%E9%99%B5%E8%98%AD%E9%81%94%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E7%9A%84-%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6-%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E5%85%88%E5%89%8D%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E7%9A%84%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85-195112585.html",
